arStrings.szText: Casting a {c_important}Mastery, Weapon Mastery, Macabre, Wrath,{/c} or {c_important}Imbuement{/c} Skill calls a {c_important}Bat Familiar{/c} to attack nearby enemies, dealing {c_random}[SF_9|0] - [SF_10|0]{/c} {c_advanced}[[SF_11|0]%]{/c} Physical damage with a {c_number}[SF_5|1]%{/c} chance to Stun.
